---
title: Creamy Chicken, Mushroom, Spinach & Ricotta Ravioli with Rocket Salad
description: Ready in less than 25 minutes, this Creamy Chicken, Mushroom, Spinach & Ricotta Ravioli is quick and full of flavour. Make an easy, cheesy sauce that's flavoured with herbs and the earthiness of the mushrooms to pair with the creamy filling of the pasta.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R43_W45_UK_QV20193-8_Main_low-3c55b86b.jpg
